{"tid":658574,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"香港政府嘅 email 系統將由中國公司全面接管","createTime":"2018-05-09T05:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T13:21:15.000Z","uid":1886,"like":108,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"b6979e30c0687f65da9092cb18550b283b9821e7","tid":658574,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/135354_ed3b1b979420c3e4e9c7ce0cdb29f274.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F135354_ed3b1b979420c3e4e9c7ce0cdb29f274.png&h=553a45e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港政府嘅 email 一直都係用 Exchange 或者 Domino 相信好多人都知，不過呢個即將會成為歷史喇，因為創科局早前出咗張 Tender 將所有唔同部門嘅 email 系統整合，俾一間叫「彩訊」嘅深圳公司中標，全部搬曬去一個叫RichMail 嘅國產系統，盛惠 2 億 3 千萬，相信日後所有資料都會直送中央，除咗恭喜之外我都唔知講乜好呀 &hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n連埋原本張 Tender 畀大家參考：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ogcio.gov.hk/en/our_work/business/tender_eoi_rfp/doc/GCIO-055-074-002-001-Tender(v1.2).zip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ogcio.gov.hk%2Fen%2Four_work%2Fbusiness%2Ftender_eoi_rfp%2Fdoc%2FGCIO-055-074-002-001-Tender%28v1.2%29.zip&d=6vip%2FWGl7S7zQQV9HxwY4AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ebe6266e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ogcio.gov.hk/en/our_work/business/tender_eoi_rfp/doc/GCIO-055-074-002-001-Tender(v1.2).zip</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/1888741734498884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fposts%2F1888741734498884&d=6vip%2FWGl7S7zQQV9HxwY4AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e327ae95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/1888741734498884</a>"},{"pid":"35c5a1108253ebf4bff2e73f5438f75fd2d24035","tid":658574,"uid":52090,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"repl